    "description": {
      "content": "The Mailtrap Email Sending API allows sending transactional and bulk emails with high deliverability. It follows REST principles and supports authentication via API tokens, with all requests sent over HTTPS. The API exposes a JSON-based send endpoint and a batch endpoint capable of delivering up to 500 emails in a single request.\n\nContact Support:\n Name: Mailtrap Support",
